[1mUsage:[0m
  nlc COMMAND
  nlc [COMMAND] --help | -h
  nlc --version | -v

[1mCommands:[0m
  [32mrun[0m      Run a natural language command (default)
  [32mconfig[0m   Manage configuration
  [32mprompt[0m   Manage system prompt

[1mOptions:[0m
  [32m--help, -h[0m
    Show this help

  [32m--version, -v[0m
    Show version number

[1mEnvironment Variables:[0m
  [32mNLC_CONFIG[0m
    Path to the NLC config file
    Default: ~/.nlc/config

[1mExamples:[0m
  nlc convert input.webm to output.mp4
  nlc list all docker images older than a month and delete them
